35: Really? Well, my favorite color is blue. So, you really don't have any favorite color?

38: Aha! White, a classic. White is also the safest color to have on a car. Statistically, white cars are less often involved in car accidents.
39: Black is a really smart color! It can be produced by mixing all the primary colors together.
40: Hm, grey is said to be the color of intelligence. Albert Einstein allegedly only wore grey.

42: Every color is wonderful, right? It's amazing how many colors the human eye can see.
